LOCUS       PtetA                     29 bp    DNA              UNK 01-JAN-1980
DEFINITION  Natural 29 bp Tn10 PtetA promoter: a sigma-70 -35/-10 promoter whose
            spacer holds the central 17 bp of the tetO1 operator, making
            transcription TetR/anhydrotetracycline-controllable..
